Meet top doctors from anywhere on MeetDoctor. Take complete care of yourself and your family from the comfort of your home - consult doctors online, book doctor appointments, order medicines online, and book diagnostic tests.

MeetDoctor, Cambodia’s fastest growing telemedicine app that was just built by Cambodian doctors. It is a one-stop solution for all your healthcare and medical needs where you can:

Access instant video consultation across 20+ specialties
Book doctor appointments for physical exam
Order medicines and get them delivered to your doorstep
Book lab tests and get free home sample collection
Buy family health plans for unlimited online medical consultations
Read expert-written articles and tips

Get started with just four simple steps:

1. Enter your symptoms
2. Select a specialist and pay online
3. Wait 2 minutes to connect with one of the online doctors
4. Consult via video/audio call/ chat and get online doctor advice

Find and book appointments with doctors near you

No long clinic queues. Worry no more! Choose from all specialists in Cambodia. Book appointments for Dentists, Dermatologists, Gynaecologists, Pediatricians, Psychiatrists, Urologists, Orthopedists, and more specialities.

Every doctor registered on MD Doctors  (our doctors’ app) undergoes a strict onboarding and verification process.


Order medicines online and get them delivered to your doorstep. Find any medicines, health, and wellness products on MeetDoctor’s online medicine store. Save big with discounts and offers on medicines, surgical, and other products.


You can find us on www.meetdoctor.co and https://www.facebook.com/meetdoctor 

Book doctor appointments for diabetes, cancer, weight loss, hair fall, dental, ENT problems & more. Get online medical consultations for 20+ specialities including Psychology, Physiotherapy, Gynaecology, Dermatology, Gastroenterology, Dentistry, Orthopaedics, & more..

외국인 전용! '케어해줘?' 통합 의료 서비스 앱



대한민국에서의 완벽한 의료 경험을 제공하는 '케어해줘?'에 오신 것을 환영합니다!
저희 앱은 외국인 환자들이 한국에서 언어 장벽 없이 의료 서비스를 이용할 수 있도록 도와드립니다.
서비스 범위  저희 '케어해줘?'는 다음과 같은 전문 의료 서비스를 제공합니다:
코스메틱: 피부가 더 건강하고 아름다워지길 원하시나요? 최고의 전문가가 여러분을 기다립니다! 
치과: 모든 종류의 치과 치료를 안전하고 편안하게! 
성형 외과: 자신감을 되찾고 싶으신가요? 최상의 성형 수술로 꿈을 실현하세요! 
비뇨기과 및 산부인과: 전문적이고 세심한 관리로 여러분의 건강을 최우선으로 생각합니다. 
특별한 혜택 
다국어 지원: 15개 언어 이상으로 서비스를 제공하여 언어 장벽을 해소합니다. 
무료 코디네이터 제공: 모든 외국인 고객에게 개인 코디네이터가 배정되어, 한국어에서 고객의 모국어로 통역해 드립니다. 
예약 시스템: 언제 어디서나 손쉽게 진료 예약이 가능합니다. 
실시간 채팅 및 음성 통화: 언제든지 코디네이터와 실시간으로 소통할 수 있습니다. 
쇼핑 페이지: 필요한 모든 뷰티 제품을 쉽게 구매할 수 있습니다. 

'케어해줘?'와 함께라면, 건강 관리가 더 이상 어렵지 않습니다. 지금 바로 다운로드하여 건강한 변화를 경험하세요!

Experience managing your health and well-being anytime, anywhere with Pethyoeung e-Health ID App. You can read, and understand about countless health knowledge, store and manage your previous health records, make an appointment with your doctors, and even control your personal health information in a few clicks on your phone. Through Pethyoeung e-Health ID, your health information that you wish to share can be accessed and shared anytime to any doctors, from any hospital.

Manage your Medical Records anywhere, anytime:
- After your treatment ends, every medical record will be automatically saved into your Medical History in your Mobile app.
- You can also upload your necessary medical documents and store them in the app in either JPG or PNG file. The medical record uploading is at your decision and is not required by the app.
- You can see all of your previous medical histories anywhere, anytime when needed.
- With your permission, you can share your medical records with any doctors at different hospitals.

Manage your appointment with the doctors and control your schedule
- You will have a clear reference of when and where, with which doctor you have met previously.
- The doctor can easily initiate an appointment with you, and every appointment is there for you to manage.
- You can also suggest or initiate an appointment with doctors/hospitals anytime on your mobile phone, which would then be confirmed or rejected through your personal chat box with the hospital on your App.

Your personal information is there for you to manage
- Doctors at the hospitals that use “Peth Yoeung” system will gather and know your personal information necessary for the treatment immediately if you are registered with the Pethyoeung e-Health ID App.
- Manage your personal information in the Profile Function.

Read and get health knowledge:
- Know what type of food is nutritious and good for your health.
- Know the tips on how to take care of yourself in every aspect.

Read and get the most recent news from the Ministry and other health-expertise institutions
- In cooperation with the Public Health Institutions, including the Ministry of Health Cambodia and other health-expertise institutions, our App will report on​ current public health policies, regulations, and news under the authority of those institutions.
- Every news report of this section will be the sole responsibility of the Ministry of Health and other health-specialized institutions.

No matter which hospital you go to, Pethyoeung e-Health ID is always there for you. You will no longer have to keep and carry a bunch of paper records all the time but can always manage your information right in your phone. Pethyoeung e-Health ID, we care for your health.

Data loaded in IDV (IMAIOS DICOM Viewer) isn't uploaded on the network to ensure storage safety and security of personal health information of the patients (excluding use of sharing features).
IDV supports DICOM files of all types (ultrasound, scanner, MRI, PET, etc.) and offers several fast and intuitive tools such as scrolling, image manipulation and measurement.
It allows you to easily open any file stored on your device or accessible online for quick viewing whenever you want.
Completely free for personal and non-commercial use, IDV is also accessible in its online version on the website www.imaios.com.

Caution: IDV has not been tested or certified for clinical use. It is NOT approved as a medical device. It cannot be used for primary diagnosis in medical imaging.

Discover one of the top pregnancy tracker apps designed specifically for women and expecting parents. May your pregnancy be pleasant and wonderful! Our app provides the tools and resources expecting parents need to feel confident and prepared.

- Convenient Calendar: Schedule tests and doctor visits effortlessly.

- Daily Articles: Access a wealth of resources and tools with professional advice to help women navigate emotions, relationships, and health during pregnancy.  

- Doctor Report: Compile all your tracking data into a comprehensive report, available as a PDF or on your phone, to share with your doctor.  

- Checklists and To-Do Lists: Stay organized with trimester-specific checklists and to-do lists—perfect for expecting parents.  

- Smart Gestational Age Calculator: Trusted by top medical professionals, this tool calculates fetal and obstetric terms with pinpoint accuracy.  

- Kegel Exercises: Prepare for childbirth with guided exercises, an essential tool for women’s health during pregnancy.  

- Contraction Counter: This intelligent tracker distinguishes real contractions from practice ones, ensuring you and your baby are ready for delivery.  

- Health App Synchronization: Securely save your pregnancy tracking data with seamless integration.

Does the world need another OB-wheel-due-date-calculator app?  You bet!  OB Wheels combines three things that clinicians need to derive all the dates necessary in pregnancy care, and no other app has this combination.   

It contains a calendar calculator to determine EDD (EDC) from LMP or from a sonogram report.  The calendar calculator also provides gestational age (EGA) as of any date for a given EDD or LMP.  Because the calculator works off the real calendar, it is accurate for leap years too.

Then for all of you who miss your cardboard OB wheel, the app contains one which you can rotate, pinch and zoom, and generally play with just like a regular cardboard wheel.  It's a little tricky to learn how to plant two fingers and rotate them rather than pinch-and-zoom to get rotation versus resizing.  But the wheel works and it is accurate, especially so because you can zoom in to be sure where the little date hash lines lie.

Finally, the app notes the most recent committee opinion scheme from ACOG on how one might reconcile due dates from LMP and sonograms to arrive at a single final EDD.  To my knowledge, the scheme is authority-based and no better or worse than other schemes, but my practice and my learners need a single clear scheme, so this app includes one for easy reference.

As an educator and clinician myself, I am grateful for feedback.  Email me via the contact email at my website.
